  ARTIFICIAL INTELLIGENCE & MACHINE LEARNING
============================================================

Concept:     Reinforcement Learning
Category:    Paradigm
Definition:  Agent learns from environment interaction to maximize reward
Year:        1950
Researchers: Bellman; Sutton/Barto
Applications:Games, robotics, recommendations, LLM alignment
Related:     Reward, policy, value function, Q-learning

Concept:     Diffusion Model
Category:    Architecture
Definition:  Learns to reverse a noise-adding process for generation
Year:        2020
Researchers: Ho et al.
Applications:Image/video/audio generation (Stable Diffusion)
Related:     DDPM, score matching, noise schedule

Concept:     Constitutional AI
Category:    Alignment
Definition:  AI trained on principles via self-critique to reduce harm
Year:        2022
Researchers: Anthropic/Bai et al.
Applications:Claude safety and alignment
Related:     RLHF, harmlessness, helpfulness, honesty

